    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>oven-baked honey & soy beef </strong>topped with your <strong>toasted sesame seeds</strong> and <strong>chopped spring onion</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> sesame rice </strong>to the side</p><p>Dig in!</p>",
